Acked-by: Mika Westerberg <mika.westerberg@linux.intel.com>
Acked-by: Andy Shevchenko <andriy.shevchenko@linux.intel.com>
Tested-by: Roman Gilg <subdiff@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Lee Jones <lee.jones@linaro.org>
